code: @Override public CMSAttributeTableGenerator getAttributesGenerator(Exchange excange) throws CryptoCmsException {     Hashtable<ASN1ObjectIdentifier, Attribute> attrs = new Hashtable<>().     attrs.put(PKCSObjectIdentifiers.id_aa_contentHint, new Attribute(PKCSObjectIdentifiers.id_aa_contentHint, new DERSet(new DERUTF8String("Hint")))).     attrs.put(PKCSObjectIdentifiers.id_aa_receiptRequest, new Attribute(PKCSObjectIdentifiers.id_aa_receiptRequest, new DERSet(new DERUTF8String("Request")))).     AttributeTable attrTable = new AttributeTable(attrs).     return new SimpleAttributeTableGenerator(attrTable). }
